{"tid":104093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警 員 涉 不小心駕駛及妨礙司法公正  被 捕","createTime":"2017-02-01T20:26:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T06:25:47.000Z","uid":62257,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dac59a1efd408c1e40a75c5c7b120e255447c027","tid":104093,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T20:26:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?SearchText=&amp;NewsId=20170201222341&amp;page=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FSearchText%3D%26NewsId%3D20170201222341%26page%3D0&d=HVFDXqn9keSrFxh6Mt7Td2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=06609676\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?SearchText=&amp;NewsId=20170201222341&amp;page=0</a><br />\n1/2/2017 22:23<br />\n        一名男警員涉嫌不小心駕駛及妨礙司法公正, 被警方拘捕, 明日在觀塘裁判法院提堂.<br />\n        警方說, 被捕警員在去年八月執行職務期間駕駛車輛, 撞倒一個水龍頭, 但他涉嫌訛稱事發經過. 東九龍總區重案組接手調查, 並經徵詢法律意見, 今日在秀茂坪區拘捕他.<br />\n        警方重申, 警隊非常重視人員的操守, 任何人員干犯違法行為, 絕不容忍和姑息, 定必嚴正處理. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=921006&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D921006%26csid%3D261_341&d=HVFDXqn9keSrFxh6Mt7Td2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=1dee9030\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=921006&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n01.02.2017 22:50<br />\n警方在秀茂坪拘捕一名四十一歲駐守秀茂坪的軍裝警員，涉嫌去年八月在駕駛警車執勤期間，不小心駕駛，撞毀一個水龍頭，但事後又向上級訛稱事發經過，涉嫌提供假口供，妨礙司法公正，重案組經調查後感到可疑，經徵詢法律意見後，將他拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理。"},{"pid":"225ac823d940ee74384804910c6e3c10e7a365f3","tid":104093,"uid":27146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T20:31:13.000Z","msg":"今次係當班警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67a52a038fa270a5ba4235a6ce44fbecd60e2bfb","tid":104093,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T20:33:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d186427b72c8f0676bab6cad8ec5dca66788158b","tid":104093,"uid":13835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T20:58:08.000Z","msg":"警方表示，非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理。<br />\n呢句野一年究竟可以見幾多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa8f1b8cd485118109e0ad5cfde88a17af50401","tid":104093,"uid":29874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T21:50:39.000Z","msg":"係咪前排屈人刑毁嗰單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ac3c326c591f8461f72dd39aedee4bd6140204","tid":104093,"uid":10922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T01:29:41.000Z","msg":"goal！！！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"677f6d960975b1c1835fb6a069d02238bebb35bf","tid":104093,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T01:32:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不</span></span>"},{"pid":"b3495d7d1f89cf6d2c20e7cea257b603c2beca94","tid":104093,"uid":4326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T01:34:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>警方表示，非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理。<br />\n呢句野一年究竟可以見幾多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nTemplate 黎架<br />\n<br />\n每段醜聞後邊自動落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba2e4f8de90fcf6961945ac5c8643a779d56f621","tid":104093,"uid":77731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T01:39:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>警方表示，非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理。<br />\n呢句野一年究竟可以見幾多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/